 ►CVideoEntityA helper class that provides an aggregation of all video entity types. Users can ask Alexa to search for video content by specifying characteristics of the content, such as a season and episode of a TV show, or a genre of movie. Alexa sends these characteristics, called entity types for searching the requested content. This class also provides methods to parse the entity payload into respective types
